# Cloudflare Pages — URL redirects
# Format: source  destination  [status]

# Redirect www → apex (301 permanent)
https://www.example.com/*  https://example.com/:splat  301

# Convenience shortlinks (use in email signatures, bios, etc.)
/linkedin   https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile   302
/mentor     https://example.com/mentoring         302
/medium     https://medium.com/@yourhandle        302
/twitter    https://x.com/yourhandle              302
/x          https://x.com/yourhandle              302
